com.theif519.sakoverlay.Core.Adapters

Class VideoInfoAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • <any>
      • com.theif519.sakoverlay.Widgets.Adapters.VideoInfoAdapter

  • public class VideoInfoAdapter
extends <any>
    Created by theif519 on 11/19/2015.

    The adapter to hold the VideoInfo data, used to hold various information like the thumbnail bitmap, the duration, name, etc. It implements the ViewHolder pattern which is the standard for adapters in Android, and overall is mostly boiler plate code.
